{"tid":2141724,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"巨龍損首，我屌埋你老母！","createTime":"2020-08-06T02:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T09:15:34.000Z","uid":32051,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"536f42dd52cf13b2559a0c4358b6a6d078cdadf2","tid":2141724,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4AwPfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4AwPfW.png&h=fa653075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">食死貓咪食囉</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你真係唔怕回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁樣講得出，到時你同你家人受到乜野不公義時，人地大返你依句，就可以無負擔咁屌鳩你。<br />\n屌得啱就啱，屌錯你？Sor，你食死貓咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龍門忍撚左差唔多成年，你班撚樣默默容許渣狗朋黨對佢既攻擊，到龍門還擊就出嚟叫佢停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班撚樣真係枉為人。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地有仔女，我祝佢地一生一世俾人欺凌，幼稚園蝦到上中學。<br />\n到佢地還擊果陣俾老師屌佢地以暴易暴唔啱，然後佢地一個二個含冤跳樓死。"},{"pid":"874ea9eba5ac1136ff0ef477ab9b392be74be56b","tid":2141724,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:30:00.000Z","msg":"岩啦 拿拿聲出黎一齊批鬥佢食沙津啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878d19ce6d6fd8cfca1722a0d90355641d41880d","tid":2141724,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:31:42.000Z","msg":"高調聲稱自己 請人去「台灣旅行」會否被國安法檢控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acded7640e7b56f3d03e912793483102183f181","tid":2141724,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"五毛繼續分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續扮 極端龍門派 vs 極端反龍門派"},{"pid":"e838aab6583042df42fe3741e44afb4d2c3885d0","tid":2141724,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020